{"tid":345748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士司機猝死車內","createTime":"2017-08-03T10:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:40:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4137e33bfdbd7c18a54dd14f9d908dbdf07b8d26","tid":345748,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20110011&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20110011%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170803&d=9R5E9CeSmXhEJAbl7%2BgU%2FNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=5d69400d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20110011%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170803&h=50311ed7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20110011&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170803</a><br />\n<br />\n的士司機猝死車內<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170803/large/03la8p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170803%2Flarge%2F03la8p02.jpg&h=3747f402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司機昏倒於司機位，惟送院已告不治。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】58歲的士司機昨中午駕空載的士駛經上環干諾道西時，疑因身體不適，將的士停於路旁巴士站後昏倒駕駛座位，途人發現報警，警員及救護員到場將他送院，證實已不治。警方調查後懷疑他心臟病發猝死，為一個多月來第二名開工期間猝死的士司機。<br />\n死者樊錦明，據悉樊有心臟病紀錄，事發昨中午12時35分，樊駕駛無載客的士沿干諾道西往堅尼地城方向，當駛至皇后街附近時，疑樊感到身體不適，立即將的士駛至巴士站休息，惟他未幾卻陷入昏迷，途人發現致電報警，警員及救護員到場，替他急救後送院，惜已回天乏術。警員在車內未有發現違禁藥物，聯絡其家人協助調查，獲悉他患有心臟病，不排除他開工期間突然心臟病發猝死，案件並無可疑，真正死因有待剖屍確定。<br />\n上月1日，每日工作15小時49歲姓李的士司機，當日發燒抱病開工期間致電妻子稱不適後失聯，家人報警求助及四處找尋，其後在西環皇后大道西尋獲事主之的士，發現他昏倒車內送院不治。<br />\n■記者翁鈺輝、黃麗英"},{"pid":"0a4bbad0a8e170c3f1cfb8e836b3558e87624c36","tid":345748,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"終於唔係好爸爸 經濟支柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13f79c7c99a57e795841b075fea414968590373","tid":345748,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"帶病仲做15 粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}